data.text: @hEnereyG Liberal intellectuals are only prepared to deal with Johnny Hatemonger and Charlie Biblethump. In being media savvy they can’t help but see Bannon as one of them like this was high school debate club.

Steve Bannon is a pile of rotting meat out to kill/imprison as many people as possible before he dies of a cocaine overdose BUT the guy works in the press, he knows all the Sorkin-like “excuse me, sir” gotchas from high school debate club & will just laugh all the way to the bank

All these press dinguses are really just mad they can’t live out their West Wing/Newsroom fanfic of finally defeating a fascist through decorum & facts. That shit is a tv show, it’s not real, and if that worked on Steve Bannon he wouldn’t be super rich off of Breitbart
